node.text:
Thanks for the feast. 
Enjoying exotic flavours from @sgdeliveryonline . Had a taste of world flavours with dishes from restaurants featuring @cubalibre.sg (Latin American), @sggabbar (Indian), @shabestan.sg ( Persian) and @pitatreekitchenandbar (Mediterranean).
4 different cuisines on one convenient platform . 
An absolute delight ! 
#thewackyduo #shabestan #pitatree #gabbar #cubalibre #exoticfood #circuitbreakermeal #circuitbreakersg #circuitbreakerdelivery
